WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.879
Hey, good morning everybody again.

00:00:03.164 --> 00:00:06.034
I'm going to do another video here; I'm doing them back to back.

00:00:06.617 --> 00:00:10.791
This is something the Lord brought to my attention yesterday in my prayer time.

00:00:10.791 --> 00:00:31.506
He told me that in the summer of 2022—I believe it was about this time last year, well, a little bit before because it was probably around April or so—he came to me when I was praying and said, 'Brandon, there's going to be a massive increase in the near future coming up.

00:00:31.506 --> 00:00:35.399
Oil is going to go to $200 a barrel.

00:00:35.399 --> 00:00:46.260
' He said the Prince of Saudi Arabia is going to go against the United States, and they're going to cause an oil shortage.

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:55.594
They're going to go with Russia and China in this, and it's like a secret mission against the United States.

00:00:55.594 --> 00:01:03.149
But I saw the price of gas go to almost seven dollars a gallon again.

00:01:03.149 --> 00:01:09.180
I saw things like the price of commodities rising because they're trying to control inflation.

00:01:11.489 --> 00:01:19.645
This is all part of the global economic reset; it's part of the digital platform they're doing—creating new digital currencies and weakening the dollar.

00:01:28.273 --> 00:01:33.567
I don't know how all this happens; I'm just saying these are the parts that I see.

00:01:33.567 --> 00:01:45.247
The Lord told me that, like I said, oil would go to $200 a barrel and gas was going to go very, very high, so I just wanted to warn you about some of this stuff.

00:01:45.247 --> 00:01:49.004
Number two: this was three or four weeks ago, I believe.

00:01:49.004 --> 00:01:55.860
I was praying and the Lord showed me, 'I need you to pray for Italy.

00:01:55.860 --> 00:01:59.059
' I said, 'What's going on with Italy, Lord?

00:01:59.059 --> 00:02:04.433
' and he showed me—I had an open-eye vision again—that there's a massive volcano that's about to happen.

00:02:06.855 --> 00:02:13.294
I saw a coastline on the water, and there's a massive volcano there.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:21.120
He told me this is going to happen, and he said there will be signs right before there's a massive explosion.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:28.290
I saw it explode huge, and he kept having me pray over the ocean.

00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:43.000
There's something about the water around Italy that is very dangerous; there's like a volcano in that water, and this is going to shoot off and cause major devastation.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.495
It's going to be very serious.

00:02:46.245 --> 00:02:49.514
I've been praying for the people of Italy to wake up.

00:02:49.514 --> 00:02:56.588
If they are Christian—or if they're not—pray that they are where they're supposed to be so that they will leave when this thing goes off.

00:02:56.970 --> 00:03:05.940
There's a huge town or city on the edge of the water where I saw this volcano go off.

00:03:05.940 --> 00:03:23.213
There will be signs, maybe even on the news in Italy, about some rumblings around that area—some earthquakes or tremors—to pre-warn that something big is going to happen.

00:03:23.213 --> 00:03:24.885
Do not ignore this.

00:03:26.265 --> 00:03:30.450
It is very serious; what I saw is very serious.

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:41.713
If you have little tremors, if you start having a lot of tremors, and you start seeing smoke or there's something going on, take heed.

00:03:42.686 --> 00:03:48.820
Be forewarned; I'm trying to tell you this is going to be a major event, an end-time event.

00:03:49.875 --> 00:03:54.059
I don't know when it's going to happen; I wish I did.

00:03:54.059 --> 00:04:01.429
I'm sorry; I only see in part and I hear in part, and so it's just stuff I'm praying over.

00:04:01.429 --> 00:04:04.050
That's basically what I had; those are two little things.

00:04:05.085 --> 00:04:12.023
I have another video I'm about to do; it'll be my third video, but this is the positive one.

00:04:12.023 --> 00:04:14.756
Have a blessed day.

00:04:14.756 --> 00:04:15.439
Bye-bye.
